# PLACEHOLDER — no real certificate is shipped in this template.
# The gateway TLS cert/key are GENERATED per-brain at deploy time by
# system/brain_bin/gateway/gen-cert.sh (a self-signed cert), landing as tls/cert.key + tls/cert.key.
# Never commit a real cert.key/cert.key to the factory. Run gen-cert.sh (or supply your own
# CA-issued pair) during provisioning; the wsl/apply.manifest maps them into the brain.
